,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"一早BLOCK左樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />典型冇SOURCE亂作FAKE NEWS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447c908bc64a78be773d500b34f718bc3332a3f0","tid":2099043,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"forbes: <br />\nIt&rsquo;s important also to note that this research has not yet been peer reviewed, which is a key part of the scientific vetting process prior to publication in a journal. However, given the need for information on the origin and spread of the pandemic, many scientists are publicly sharing and promoting their data prior to publication, but it should still be treated as preliminary and taken with a grain of salt.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theconversation.com/was-coronavirus-really-in-europe-in-march-2019-141582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fwas-coronavirus-really-in-europe-in-march-2019-141582&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDKxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=2a698401\" target=\"_blank\">https://theconversation.com/was-coronavirus-really-in-europe-in-march-2019-141582</a>:<br />\nThere are several explanations for this positive result. One is that SARS-CoV-2 is present in the sewage at a very low level. Another is that the test reaction was accidentally contaminated with SARS-CoV-2 in the laboratory. This sometimes happens in labs as positive samples are regularly being handled, and it can be difficult to prevent very small traces of positive sample contaminating others.<br />\n<br />\nAnother explanation is that there is other RNA or DNA in the sample that resembles the test target site enough for it to give a positive result at the 39th cycle of amplification.<br />\n<br />\nFurther tests need to be carried out to conclude that the sample contains SARS-CoV-2, and a finding of that magnitude would need to be replicated separately by independent laboratories."},{"pid":"45a803a6218dee910b313de84f15c78d73642785","tid":2099043,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:48:15.000Z","msg":"看圖作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c4a1eb5dd94abf57aef109b29aa0b236dbb224","tid":2099043,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"想問咩叫甩鍋？"},{"pid":"e80997116adfac2a27b9ddc45e8d160e766476a3","tid":2099043,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"139bfa27382702494fc3e9820aa18616d24c7228","tid":2099043,"uid":24582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"561c29d4dd79e303d45a33fa9f59e9bf6cfae428","tid":2099043,"uid":176313,"like":59,"dislike":7,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"宜家啲五毛洗板技术真係越嚟越粗劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:18:22.000Z","msg":"技術？<br />\n技术？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:59:17.000Z","msg":"五毛po用殘體屌，費事屌完佢哋睇唔明啦"},{"pid":"ae73c578f79b9ee5a85211ebf86a6593f84fe350","tid":2099043,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:59:46.000Z","msg":"當呢度高登呀屌你"},{"pid":"34b8054bde58dcc8c9b8929da19aedb0867ce18a","tid":2099043,"uid":22888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"睇完只係覺得 中國欠美國一個道歉"},{"pid":"8e3cb910fe73f3695032a54dc06a998635e4b6bc","tid":2099043,"uid":250557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:00:54.000Z","msg":"咁嘅垃圾都放出嚟"},{"pid":"e801040f10b1eb998eb128840ff796cc7378410c","tid":2099043,"uid":138144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5LwDj3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5LwDj3D.png&h=6